Text: Hello. i am a mother who had not travelled this world but travelled each and
  every phase of life. my vocabullary for english words is short so u wont get much
  new things from me but i ll try to speak. we should live our life like it can may
  be our last day of our life. life is short plz enjoy. i dnt know much about writting
  but i had experince of lyf n its too hard to live this life in this era. if i got
  this scholarship i ll want this job to be do. i love eating. i dnt have much money
  to go out n try new dishes but i am honest if i eat something n i dont like it i
  speak it out. i  belong to hindu family where we were not allowded to eat non veg
  but when i got to marry muslim family they were proper into non vegetrain dishes.
  my 1st favorite non veg dish ever can be tandoori chicken.n thats when i went on
  and on. all the way to non veg. its like my very great experince towards new dishes.
